				<h1>Live-in</h1>
				<!--#include virtual="/includes/virginia-story.inc"-->
				<p>4 out of 5 older adults say they would prefer to remain at home as they age. <span class='uppercase'>Bayada</span> specializes in providing comprehensive live-in home health care services. Live-in services are a great option for those who need assistance with daily activities throughout the day.  Live-in services provide security and peace of mind for both the clients and their families by providing individualized services while preserving independence and dignity.</p>

				<h2>Cost-effective care at home</h2>
				<p>Live-in care can be a cost effective alternative to a nursing home. Our health care team includes home health aides*, certified nursing assistants, homemakers, or companions, professionals who are dedicated to providing care with compassion, excellence, and reliability.</p>

				<h2>Live-in services include:</h2>
					<ul>
						<li>Bathing, dressing, grooming, and toileting</li>
						<li>Help with meals and nutrition</li>
						<li>Light housekeeping, such as vacuuming, dusting, and sweeping</li>
						<li>Assistance with mobility (including the use of walkers, wheelchairs, or lifts)</li>
						<li>Shopping for groceries</li>
						<li>Prescription pick-up and medication reminders</li>
						<li>Running errands</li>
						<li>Escorting to appointments</li>
						<li>Companionship and leisure activities ( such as, games, crafts, and reading)</li>
		            		</ul><br>

